name: Track Side Life Issue 1
description:
Currently sold out!  My car was broken into in Oakland; they took my zines and laptop which had half of the next issue on it.  Luckily I have issue one on a USB drive and I will print more soon, so check back.  If you would like to order a quantity or just donate to my cause drop me a line and I will get back to you.

Black and white, 38 page zine featuring lots of freight train graffiti, an interview with ASIC ETC and a freight hopping story with photos.
Boxcars, gondolas, reefers, autoracks, tankers, well cars, grainers, cabooses.  Old stuff, new stuff, monikers, wholecars, characters!

DOWN FOR TRADES
I will trade for paint, collectible paint, railroad stuff, beer, etc.
I travel all over the US and may be coming to your town soon.
So get ahold of me and let me know!

Tracksidelife@yahoo.com or contact through BigCartel
